Texts.Chs: 把^orange;遗传物质^reset;带回^orange;科学前哨站^reset;给^green;我^reset;。
Texts.Eng: Bring the ^green;Genetic Material^reset; to ^orange;me^reset; at the ^orange;Science Outpost^reset;

Texts.Chs: 不仅仅是肉类，遗传物质来自许多东西。只需要记住，只要是生存着的细胞结构的生物，那么它里面很可能就会存在一些遗传物质。
Texts.Eng: Genetic material comes from many things, not just meat. Remember that if it is alive and full of cells, it just might give you some.

Texts.Chs: ^orange;肉^reset;非常美味用途也很广。试着把肉放到物质萃取器里，并将产生物带给我。
Texts.Eng: ^orange;Meat^reset; is both delicious and useful. ^orange;Extract some meat^reset; and bring me 5 of the results.
